=== REMAPS ===

vnoremap S( c()<Esc>P
vnoremap S{ c{}<Esc>P
vnoremap S[ c[]<Esc>P

" Centers the screen after paging down/up
nnoremap <C-d> <C-d>zz
nnoremap <C-u> <C-u>zz

" Window/Views navigation remaps
nnoremap <space>vs :vsc View.SolutionExplorer<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vc :vsc View.GitHub.Copilot.Chat<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vg :vsc View.GitWindow<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vr :vsc View.GitRepositoryWindow<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vo :vsc View.Output<Enter>
nnoremap <space>v' :vsc View.Terminal<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vt :vsc View.TaskList<Enter>
nnoremap <space>vx :vsc View.Toolbox<Enter>


" Document group remaps
nnoremap <space>wn :vsc View.NavigateForward<Enter>
nnoremap <space>wp :vsc View.NavigateBackward<Enter>
nnoremap <space>wv :vsc Window.NewVerticalTabGroup<Enter>
nnoremap <space>wl :vsc Window.MoveToNextTabGroup<Enter>
nnoremap <space>wh :vsc Window.MoveToPreviousTabGroup<Enter>
nnoremap <space>ww :vsc Window.MoveToMainDocumentGroup<Enter>
nnoremap <space>wa :vsc File.CloseOtherTabs<Enter>

" Files, Documents, Classes remaps
nnoremap <space>nc :vsc Project.AddClass<Enter>
nnoremap <space>nf :vsc Project.NewFolder<Enter>

" Error list remaps
nnoremap <space>ee :vsc View.ErrorList<Enter>
nnoremap <space>en :vsc View.NextError<Enter>
nnoremap <space>ep :vsc View.PreviousError<Enter>

" Refactoring remaps
nnoremap <space>rr :vsc Refactor.Rename<Enter>
nnoremap <space>rf :vsc Edit.FormatDocument<Enter>

" Build remaps
nnoremap <space>bb :vsc Build.BuildSolution<Enter>
nnoremap <space>bc :vsc Build.CleanSolution<Enter>
nnoremap <space>br :vsc Build.RebuildSolution<Enter>
nnoremap <space>bd :vsc Debug.Start<Enter>
nnoremap <space>bw :vsc Debug.StartWithoutDebugging<Enter>
nnoremap <space>bq :vsc Debug.StopDebugging<Enter>

" Quick actions remaps
nnoremap <space>. :vsc View.QuickActionsForPosition<Enter>

=== SETTINGS ===

" Allow copy and pasting from regular clipboard
set clipboard=unnamed

set number

" Relative numbering of lines
set relativenumber

" Do not let cursor scroll below or above N number of lines when scrolling.
set scrolloff=10

" Use highlighting when doing a search.
set hlsearch

" Set the commands to save in history default number is 20.
set history=1000

